name: Dino Kitchen Cleanup
description:
You are a dinosaur. A kitchen cleaning dinosaur! Clean the kitchen quickly before time runs out, or you will go extinct!

(again, this was made very quickly with the purpose of completing a simple game)

Controls:

WASD or Arrow Keys to move.

Space or Left Click to shoot.

Click on the "?" button in the start menu for more info. (or look at screenshot)
